# ============================================================================
# Edge Terminal — external data provider API keys
# Copy to .env.local for local dev, or set these in your Vercel project:
#   Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables (Production + Preview)
# All keys are OPTIONAL. Without them the app falls back to keyless public
# sources (Yahoo / Binance / CoinGecko) so the dashboard always renders.
# ============================================================================

# Financial Modeling Prep — powers the AI Stocks tab (Layers 1-4) + Daily Brief.
# Upgrades to real data:
#   • Quotes & daily candles            (/api/v3/quote, /api/v3/historical-price-full)
#   • Layer 3 guidance quality          (/api/v3/analyst-estimates — FY+1/FY+2 EPS)
#   • Layer 3 beat-and-raise trajectory (/api/v3/earnings-surprises)
#   • Earnings catalysts (≤10d)         (quote.earningsAnnouncement)
#   • Layer 2 bottleneck phase          (/api/v3/earning_call_transcript — MSFT/GOOGL/AMZN/META/ORCL)
# Get a key: https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/developer/docs
# Note: exact 30/60/90-day EPS-revision deltas need an estimate-history /
# SPG (S&P Global Visible Alpha) as-of-date feed; without it that one sub-score
# stays a price-trend proxy. Wire it in app/api/stocks/route.ts → fmpFundamentals().
FMP_API_KEY=

# CoinAPI.io — powers the Perps & Futures tab + Altcoin Squeeze C1 funding.
# US-accessible derivatives metrics (alternative to geo-restricted Binance):
#   • Funding rate   (metric DERIVATIVES_FUNDING_RATE_CURRENT, Binance USDⓈ-M perps)
#   • Open interest  (metric DERIVATIVES_OPEN_INTEREST) — priced via CoinGecko for USD OI
# Endpoint: GET https://rest.coinapi.io/v1/metrics/symbol/current
#           ?metric_id=...&exchange_id=BINANCEFTS   (header auth: X-CoinAPI-Key)
# Get a key: https://www.coinapi.io/  ·  Note: free tier is ~100 requests/day, so the
# routes cache aggressively (120s). Liquidation magnitude isn't in CoinAPI's current
# metrics, so Altcoin Squeeze C2/C7 stay volume/price proxies.
# Canonical var is COINAPI_KEY (COINAPI_API_KEY / COIN_API_KEY are also accepted).
COINAPI_KEY=
